Public Domain

The Rider-Waite-Smith tarot deck was first published in 1909 by
William Rider & Son of London. Both the card designs by Pamela
Colman Smith and the accompanying text by Arthur Edward Waite are
in the public domain.

Authors: A.E. Waite & Pamela Colman Smith
Source: https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Category:Rider-Waite_tarot_deck

The card descriptions in this deck are original interpretive
summaries, not reproductions of any copyrighted work.
